		<td><b>write data to w-ram</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Does any one know how to write .sav file to s-ram and w-ram on cartridge?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Author:&nbsp;</td>
