	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Using a chip clip is the best way I can think.  You'd want to power the cart edge with 5V though that way you weren't running off battery power during programming.  It's kind of a hack job idea though.  Lots of effort with all those wires and high chance of failure...

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


